  * Revert 11410, adjust new manpage to be in line with work done pre-r11410.
  * Really overhaul script, mostly code style and flow.
  * Some API incompatible changes, to force improvement from gui:
    - no more --toram, --lang or --persist options
    - no storing of exit value in tmp file
  * Merge in bits from 11410.
  * Fix broken if block.
  * Expand awk code for readability.
  * Improve awk blobs used for fdisk parsing.
  * Use LC_ALL=C when parsing external program output.
  * Remove whitespace which caused sh syntax error!
